</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubamilbanebringer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bamil Banebringer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(6/23/01 2:32:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lodizal</span><hr size=1> Heh... aye... gnoll thing was fixed Swmy. I have heard of 1 group killing the turtle easily but they were all 58+. I think 2 55+ groups would be sufficient. He doesn't last long though so you'd have to mobilize your forces quick and engage. If he's up and you need my help shoot me a tell and let's get it organized and try him.<br>
