Ten; and what about Naomi??<br>
<br>
Myriah <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uswmaestrosheerwill.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Swmaestro Sheerwill</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFF00>(6/24/01 8:39:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lodizal</span><hr size=1> One; is he a rare spawn?<br>
Yes<br>
<br>
Two; when does he spawn, is it random, is it triggered, is it timed?<br>
Random<br>
<br>
Three; where in Iceclad does he spawn?<br>
By the gnolls<br>
<br>
Four; is he immune to spells? Can the other turtle be charmed and used to tank him?<br>
I think hes 100% MR, although I've heard of him being slowed. Probably can charm the little guy too.<br>
<br>
Five; are there faction hits for killing him? <br>
Nope<br>
<br>
Six; as greed is a great motivator in the game. What items does he drop, stats?<br>
Aside from always dropping (at least?) 4 velious 55+ spells, he drops:<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics15/knotted_turtlebone_ring.JPG"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
